  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">For With their final Firelight grant, Ubumwe provides support for 30 families to engage in livestock rearing and potato farming and assists 20 additional families with start up costs to begin trading their food products. Ubumwe has identified pig rearing and potato farming as activities that have a rapid return on investment, which they note is important for families who are already dealing with poverty. By helping them to establish a stable source of food and income, Ubumwe empowers and encourages families to meet the educational and health needs of their own children</narrative>
